        "ROB_MRGREEN_BODY_NAME": "Mr. Green",
        "ROB_MRGREEN_BODY_DESCRIPTION": "Mr. Green<color=#CCD3E0>\n\n< ! > Gladius est utilis in plurimis rebus; Caestus Pugiles meliores sunt ad hostes validiores contundendos.\n\n< ! > Pistola potens est contra hostes aereos, cum brevi mora et magno damno.\n\n< ! > Volutatio munimentum armaturae paulisper relinquit et impetum audaciorem adiuvat.\n\n< ! > Bomba turbas hostium facile delere potest.</color>",
        "ROB_MRGREEN_BODY_SUBTITLE": "Ille",
        "ROB_MRGREEN_BODY_LORE": "Historia exempli pars secunda",
        "ROB_MRGREEN_BODY_OUTRO_FLAVOR": "..atque ita discessit, textu inferiore.",
        "ROB_MRGREEN_BODY_DEFAULT_SKIN_NAME": "Defalta",
        "ROB_MRGREEN_BODY_PASSIVE_NAME": "Passivum Mr. Green",
        "ROB_MRGREEN_BODY_PASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "Textus exempli.",
        "ROB_MRGREEN_BODY_PRIMARY_PUNCH_NAME": "Artes Martiales",
        "ROB_MRGREEN_BODY_PRIMARY_PUNCH_DESCRIPTION": "Celerem seriem pugnis calcibusque fac pro <style=cIsDamage>90% damno</style>.",
        "ROB_MRGREEN_BODY_SECONDARY_CLONETHROW_NAME": "Iactus Clonis",
        "ROB_MRGREEN_BODY_SECONDARY_CLONETHROW_DESCRIPTION": "Clonem invoca et ante iace, hostes propinquos rapiens et in terram pro <style=cIsDamage>420% damno</style> allidens.",
        "ROB_MRGREEN_BODY_UTILITY_DASH_NAME": "People's Elbow",
        "ROB_MRGREEN_BODY_UTILITY_DASH_DESCRIPTION": "Breve spatium impelle. Cum <style=cIsUtility>clone</style> tangis, in aerem salis et valido <style=cIsUtility>cubiti ictu</style> descendes pro <style=cIsDamage>800% damno</style>.",
        "ROB_MRGREEN_BODY_SPECIAL_RES_NAME": "Resurrection",
        "ROB_MRGREEN_BODY_SPECIAL_RES_DESCRIPTION": "Omnes clones lapsos revivisce.",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_NAME": "Nemesis Henry",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_DESCRIPTION": "Nemesis Henry est gladiator instabilis qui gladium singularem gerit, energiam servans ut impetus augeat. Moras ordinarias non habet, sed energiam sapienter regere debet.<color=#CCD3E0>\n\n< ! > Sword Mode energiam aedificat; Gun Mode energiam in impetus potentes consumit.\n\n< ! > Swordmaster onerari potest ut plus damni faciat.\n\n< ! > Flash Step instrumentum infestum potens est quod energiam aedificare adiuvat.\n\n< ! > Hydra Bite utere ut sanus maneas et Hyper Beam ut magnum damnum effundas.</color>",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_SUBTITLE": "Lapsus",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_LORE": "Historia exempli",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_OUTRO_FLAVOR": "..atque ita discessit, luna sine aperta causa deleta.",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_OUTRO_FAILURE": "..tam fortiter conatus est et tam longe pervenit. Sed in fine nihil refert.",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_DEFAULT_SKIN_NAME": "Nemesis",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_MASTERY_SKIN_NAME": "Captive #001",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_TYPHOON_SKIN_NAME": "FLLFFL",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_PASSIVE_NAME": "Gunblade Acidum",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_PASSIVE_DESCRIPTION": "Nemesis Henry arma speciale gerit quod inter Sword Mode et Gun Mode mutari potest. Artes eius moras ordinarias non habent; potius systemate <style=cIsHealing>Energiae</style> gladii nituntur.",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_PRIMARY_SPEAR_NAME": "Transfigere",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_PRIMARY_SPEAR_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>Agilis.</style> Ante te punge pro <style=cIsDamage>160% damno</style>. <style=cIsDamage>Duplex damnum facit et <style=cIsHealing>50%</style> damni dati in cuspide sanat</style>.",
        "ROB_WEAPON_SWAP_SKILL": "Weapon Swap",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_PRIMARY_SWORD_NAME": "Sword Mode",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_PRIMARY_SWORD_DESCRIPTION": "Lamina tua ante te caede pro <style=cIsDamage>280% damno</style>. In ictu <style=cIsHealing>20% Energiae</style> genera.",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_PRIMARY_GUN_NAME": "Gun Mode",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_PRIMARY_GUN_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsHealing>2.5% Energiae.</style> Iaculum penetrans <style=cIsHealing>Energiae</style> emitte pro <style=cIsDamage>240% damno</style>.",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_PRIMARY_SWORDCSS_NAME": "Sword Mode / Gun Mode",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_PRIMARY_SWORDCSS_DESCRIPTION": "Lamina tua ante te caede pro <style=cIsDamage>280% damno</style>. In ictu <style=cIsHealing>20% Energiae</style> genera.\n<style=cIsHealing>2.5% Energiae.</style> Iaculum penetrans <style=cIsHealing>Energiae</style> emitte pro <style=cIsDamage>240% damno</style>.",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_SECONDARY_BLAST_NAME": "Null Blast",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_SECONDARY_BLAST_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsUtility>Agilis.</style> Globum <style=cIsHealth>energiae arcanae</style> iace pro <style=cIsDamage>200% damno</style>.",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_SECONDARY_CHARGE_NAME": "Swordmaster",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_SECONDARY_CHARGE_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsHealing>10% Energiae.</style> In hostem propinquum impetum fac pro <style=cIsDamage>700% damno</style>. Si prope es, impetum compositum fac.",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_SECONDARY_TORRENT_NAME": "Gunslinger",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_SECONDARY_TORRENT_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsHealing>5% Energiae.</style> Seriem iaculorum <style=cIsHealing>Energiae</style> emitte. Tene ut pergat, plus <style=cIsHealing>Energiae</style> per iaculum consumens.",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_SECONDARY_CHARGECSS_NAME": "Swordmaster / Gunslinger",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_SECONDARY_CHARGECSS_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsHealing>10% Energiae.</style> In hostem propinquum impetum fac pro <style=cIsDamage>700% damno</style>.\n<style=cIsHealing>5% Energiae.</style> Seriem iaculorum <style=cIsHealing>Energiae</style> emitte.",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_UTILITY_DODGESLASH_NAME": "Caesura Celeris",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_UTILITY_DODGESLASH_DESCRIPTION": "Retro salta, hostes propinquos caedens pro <style=cIsDamage>300% damno</style>. <style=cIsUtility>Dum saltas feriri non potes.</style>",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_UTILITY_BLINK_NAME": "Flash Step",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_UTILITY_BLINK_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsHealing>5% Energiae.</style> <style=cIsUtility>Statim transi</style> ad hostem propinquum.",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_UTILITY_BURST_NAME": "Explosio Energiae",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_UTILITY_BURST_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsHealing>10% Energiae.</style> Explosum <style=cIsHealing>Energiae</style> emitte pro <style=cIsDamage>400% damno</style>, <style=cIsUtility>te vi retroacta propellens</style>.",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_UTILITY_BLINKCSS_NAME": "Flash Step / Explosio Energiae",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_UTILITY_BLINKCSS_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsHealing>5% Energiae.</style> <style=cIsUtility>Statim transi</style> ad hostem propinquum.\n<style=cIsHealing>10% Energiae.</style> Explosum <style=cIsHealing>Energiae</style> emitte pro <style=cIsDamage>400% damno</style>.",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_SPECIAL_STAB_NAME": "Hydra Bite",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_SPECIAL_STAB_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsHealing>100% Energiae.</style> Laminam tuam in hostem impinge pro <style=cIsDamage>2800% damno</style>, debuff potens inferens. <style=cIsHealing>Sana 50% damni dati.</style>",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_SPECIAL_BEAM_NAME": "Hyper Beam",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_SPECIAL_BEAM_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsHealing>100% Energiae.</style> Potentem seriem laserum para quae <style=cIsDamage>10x540% damnum</style> facit.",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_SPECIAL_STABCSS_NAME": "Hydra Bite / Hyper Beam",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_SPECIAL_STABCSS_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsHealing>100% Energiae.</style> Laminam tuam in hostem impinge pro <style=cIsDamage>2800% damno</style>, debuff potens inferens. <style=cIsHealing>Sana 50% damni dati.</style>\n<style=cIsHealing>100% Energiae.</style> Radium potentem para qui <style=cIsDamage>multum damni</style> facit.",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_UNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "???",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_UNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_DESC": "Vestigium Henrici vince.",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_UNLOCKABLE_UNLOCKABLE_NAME": "???",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_MASTERYUNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Nemesis Henry: Mastery",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_MASTERYUNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_DESC": "Ut Nemesis Henry, ludum vince aut te oblitera in Monsoon.",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_MASTERYUNLOCKABLE_UNLOCKABLE_NAME": "Nemesis Henry: Mastery",
        "ROB_NEMRY_BODY_TYPHOONUNLOCKABLE_ACHIEVEMENT_NAME": "Nemesis Henry: Grand Mastery",
